New Features:
GlobalMute -> With /globalmute; /chatmute or /mutechat you can disable the chat for everyone that don't have the Permission "yvtils.ba.bypass.mutechat".
AFKDamageKick -> With /afkdamage you can toggle the automatic kick when you get Damage, but you don't allowed to move to much otherwise you will get kicked and the Setting will disabled. When you get Damage you will get kicked and the Setting get disabled. -> Required Permission: "yvtils.ba.command.afkdamage"
Config has new Options. -> Version 8

Version 4.6.6
Status Module: Set your own Status or select one of the default, you can customize the Default Status in the Config System.
Language System: The Language System is now on the Way, I want to have good translations, so you can help to translate on a website. (Link will come with full release)

From now on every new Feature become a Version Tag and since when it is in the Plugin.

Full Changelog Version 4.6.6:
Updated for Version 1.19
Status Module → Set your own Status or selected of one of the default Status which can be set by the Server Owner.
Maintenance System is now fixed and finished and should work.
Plugin has now an own Language System with the Languages German and English, with your help there will come more. Customize 99% of the Plugin Messages
Removed the AFKKickOnDamage and Custom Crafting Recipes (CCR) CCR will come back in the Version 4.6.7 with a better Version and an own GUI
Commands like Heal or GM (Gamemode) will also be usable on other Players when Version 4.6.7 comes out.
4.6.7 Alpha 1: Updated CCR Added Sit Function Optimized Code

Version 4.6.8.1 ALPHA Changelog
» Sit Removed the ability to sit down when clicking on a stair.
» CCR Added support to craft multiple items at once. Added a new recipe; more information will follow.
» Bug Fixes
«================================»
» REWORK ANNOUNCEMENT Today, I will announce something big for this plugin! I will release Version 4.6.8.1 in full, and after that, I will start to rework the entire plugin from the beginning. I've noticed that I've lost sight of everything here, so I want to restructure, fix bugs, add long-planned features, and more.
It will probably take a while until I am finished, as I have a lot to do. But when I am finished, everything will be better—more customizability, and probably more of everything! (We will see.)
To see what is finished, it would probably be best to look on GitHub in the TODO file. I will mark everything I am done with an "x" in front of it.
Bug fixes will still be released, I think. Also, if a new minecraft version needs an update, I will try to work on it with the old code or the partially reworked code.
See you!
«================================»
» YVtils Adventures This plugin (mentioned in an older changelog) is now in the testing phase. There are still missing translations and features, but I will pause the coding progress for now and work on this plugin.
«================================»
Please report any bugs on Discord (https://yvnetwork.de/yvtils-smp/support) or through a private message to @WolfiiYV#3204.
